POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Risheeth",
  "phone": "6383781029",
  "email": "risheeth@gmail.com",
  "address_text": "Chennai"
}

###

### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users

### Get All Users (ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/admin/all 



### =========================
### PRODUCTS
### =========================

### Create Product (WITH IMAGE)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Premium Batter
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

60
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="weight"

500g
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="premium-batter.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./idly-batter.jpg
--boundary--


###

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products



### =========================
### STOCK
### =========================

### Add / Update Stock (Admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "6981f6d10e315ef28c91cbcb",
  "available_quantity": 100,
  "date": "2026-02-02"
}

###

### Get All Stock
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stock

###

### Get Stock by Date
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stock?date=2026-02-02

###

### Get Stock by Product
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stock?product_id=697f7c7db2df7d300aefd2a2

