###=========================
###DELIVERY SLOTS (MASTER)
###=========================

###Create Morning Slot (RUN ONCE)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Morning",
  "start_time": "07:00",
  "end_time": "10:00"
}

###Create Evening Slot (RUN ONCE)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/slots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Afternoon",
  "start_time": "12:00",
  "end_time": "15:00"
}

### Get All Delivery Slots
GET http://localhost:5000/api/slots

###=========================
### SLOT AVAILABILITY
###=========================

###Create Slot Availability (ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/slot-availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone_id": "6981f74e0e315ef28c91cbdc",
  "slot_id": "6981fa5c44c00eaeecfb50f0",
  "date": "2026-02-02",
  "max_orders": 20,
  "available_orders": 20
}

### Get Available Slots for Zone + Date (APP)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/slot-availability?zone_id=6981f74e0e315ef28c91cbdc&date=2026-02-02


### =========================
### ORDERS
### =========================

### FIRST: Create Slot Availability (ADMIN) - Required before placing orders
POST http://localhost:5000/api/slot-availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone_id": "6981f74e0e315ef28c91cbdc",
  "slot_id": "6981fa5c44c00eaeecfb50f0",
  "date": "2026-02-02",
  "max_orders": 20,
  "available_orders": 20
}

###

### Place New Order (USER) - Use the _id from slot availability creation above
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "6981f6a60e315ef28c91cbc4",
  "zone_id": "6981f74e0e315ef28c91cbdc",
  "slot_availability_id": "67ba1234567890abcdef1234",
  "delivery_date": "2026-02-02",
  "address_text": "Anna Nagar, Chennai",
  "payment_method": "COD",
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "6981f6d10e315ef28c91cbcb",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get All Orders (ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders

###

### Get Orders by User ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/user/6981f6a60e315ef28c91cbc4

###

### Update Order Status to CONFIRMED (ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/orders/697f87cbceff41c1ad7c2c99/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}

###

### Assign Delivery Partner to Order (ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/orders/6981fca0bf1f68ba2aeaba29/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "partnerId": "6999c873a0e39e16eacf7e0d"
}

###

### Update Order Status to OUT_FOR_DELIVERY (ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/orders/67ba1234567890abcdef5678/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "OUT_FOR_DELIVERY"
}

###

### Update Order Status to DELIVERED (ADMIN) - Releases delivery partner
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/orders/67ba1234567890abcdef5678/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "DELIVERED"
}

###

### Cancel Order (ADMIN) - Releases delivery partner if assigned
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/orders/67ba1234567890abcdef5678/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}

###


### =========================
### DELIVERY PARTNERS
### =========================

### Create Delivery Partner (ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rajesh Kumar",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "vehicle_number": "TN01AB1234",
  "zone_id": "6981f74e0e315ef28c91cbdc"
}

###

### Get All Delivery Partners (ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners

###

### Get Active + Available Partners in Zone
GET http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners?active=true&available=true&zone_id=6981f74e0e315ef28c91cbdc

###

### Get Partners by Zone
GET http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners/zone/6981f74e0e315ef28c91cbdc

###

### Get Partner by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners/6999c873a0e39e16eacf7e0d

###

### Update Partner Availability
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners/6999c873a0e39e16eacf7e0d/availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_available": true
}

###

### Update Partner Details
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners/6999c873a0e39e16eacf7e0d
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rajesh Kumar",
  "phone": "9876543211"
}

###

### Update Partner Active Status
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners/6999c873a0e39e16eacf7e0d/active
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": false
}

###

### Deactivate Partner (Soft Delete)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/delivery-partners/6999c873a0e39e16eacf7e0d

###